name: Group Set of Accessories
description:
We have teamed up with London based menswear brand Mark Thomas Taylor to create a capsule Accessories Collection.

The collection, sold as numbered sets, consits of hand woven bracelets in waxed cotton and leather as well as a chunky steel chain with a detachable indigo stone skull and matching skull keychain.

This capsule collection is super limited only 15 sets have been made

Remember to head over to markthomastaylor.com
